21 (B) (1) THERE IS A MARYLAND SOLAR PHOTOVOLTAIC MODULE
22 ENERGY SECURITY AND AFFORDABILITY FUND ADVISORY COUNCIL.
23 (2) THE COUNCIL CONSISTS OF THE FOLLOWING MEMBERS:
24 (I) FIVE REPRESENTATIVES OF THE MANUFACTURERS, RETAIL
25 SELLERS, OR INSTALLERS OF SOLAR PHOTOVOLTAIC MODULES, DESIGNATED BY
26 THE CHAIR OF THE COUNCIL;
27 (II) TWO REPRESENTATIVES OF STAKEHOLDER

