28 (3) THE COUNCIL SHALL ADMINISTER THE FUND.
29 (4) (I) THE FUND IS A SPECIAL, NONLAPSING FUND THAT IS NOT
30 SUBJECT TO § 7–302 OF THE STATE FINANCE AND PROCUREMENT ARTICLE.

